3.text: •We end a question with a question mark. e.g. :- She goes to the post office. Does she go to the post office? e.g. :- They are at home. Are they at home? •We write full stop, ✔ to show that a sentence has ended. e.g. :- Geemal is a good boy. ✔ to show that an abbreviation has ended. e.g. :- This is Mr. Siva. ✔ as a decimal point. e.g. :- We went to the canteen at 10.30 a.m.
